    "4013507": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Chiori!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Hey, you two."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are you not really into these kinds of big social occasions?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Not particularly, but this is still better than Fontaine Fashion Week."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, but if this film becomes a big hit, people will definitely come flocking to your shop!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "Yes, that's highly likely... as long as the film can premiere as planned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Are you still worried about the case?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "That, and all the obstacles we had to face today."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, you're right... It's as if all our bad luck just manifested at once."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "But why today, of all days..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chiori",
                    "T": "No... No, it's nothing. We've already delivered the film to the editors, so there should be nothing more to worry about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "How are you doing, Mr. Morris? You having a good time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Morris",
                    "T": "Well... You could say that. Do you happen to know when the party is scheduled to end?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Haha, judging by how much fun everyone's having, I'd say probably not until well after midnight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Is there something that you still have to take care of at home, Mr. Morris?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Morris",
                    "T": "Ah... I uh, I'm just not a late night person, so I might take off shortly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Oh no! Silly me, I almost forgot something super important!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Morris",
                    "T": "Oh... Uh, what is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "I prepared a whole batch of fireworks for the party, but I forgot to bring them over from the warehouse!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Morris",
                    "T": "Fireworks, you say? That's, uh, truly a pity. Sorry things didn't go as planned..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Could you help me carry them over, Mr. Morris? I won't be able to fetch all of them by myself..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Morris",
                    "T": "Me? Uh... Are you sure that you can't find anyone else?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Haha, I just wanted to make this a surprise for everyone! The warehouse isn't far from here. We'll be there in no time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "Pretty please, Mr. Morris! These are some of the best fireworks I've ever made, so I also want you to see them before you leave. They're stunning — I promise that they'll be an once-in-a-lifetime experience that you'll never forget!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Morris",
                    "T": "But..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yoimiya",
                    "T": "It's okay, just come with me! If we're sneaky enough, nobody else will see us leaving..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Morris",
                    "T": "*sigh* Oh, alright..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
