    "4013513": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Chevreuse",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Chevreuse",
                    "T": "Whoa, that felt good!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You were so fast in the water, Chevreuse... You were swimming even faster than Paimon could fly!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, about the Special Patrol... Did you join because of your dad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chevreuse",
                    "T": "Partly, but I'd say I was more inspired the heroes I read about in stories growing up."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, so it's due to your love of stories..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chevreuse",
                    "T": "Of course, it was only after I joined the Special Patrol that I learned that truth is often stranger than fiction."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chevreuse",
                    "T": "...Come on, let's walk a bit more."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
